    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scarflike capes of fur or cloth which fasten around the neck and hang down in front; includes those worn over vestments by clergy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
